description: Wannai Kinuho is Kuroko`s classmate who resides in the same dorms as Mitsuko. She is best friends with Awatsuki Maaya and together they are members of the swim club with Kinuho having the ability of aquakinesis, which gives her control over water. Kinuho was once saved from some thugs by Mikoto and is thankful to Mikoto on what she did. They are often seen hanging around Mitsuko.
name: Wannai Kinuho
